# Local-dev secrets for `npm run dev` (wrangler dev). TEMPLATE.
#
# COPY THIS FILE to `.dev.vars` and fill in the two values. `.dev.vars` is
# gitignored — never commit real secrets. These mirror the production secrets you
# set with `npx wrangler secret put HMAC_PEPPER` / `... OPERATOR_TOKEN`.
#
# Generate each as ~256 bits of URL-safe randomness:
#   openssl rand -base64 48 | tr -d '\n=' | tr '/+' '_-'

# Server pepper for HMAC-SHA256 over API key secrets. Rotating this invalidates
# every existing agent key.
HMAC_PEPPER="replace-with-a-long-random-string"

# Single operator credential — mints agents/keys, revokes documents, and backs the
# operator browser login. Rotating it also ends every operator browser session.
OPERATOR_TOKEN="replace-with-a-long-random-string"
